title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - SA342 Gazelle  - version 0.3
description:
In this video we will look at the SA342 Gazelle helicopter which has been updated to version 0.3 In this video we will look at how to install the helicopter and discuss the dependency on AirlandFS. After reviewing the exterior and cockpit we take the helicopter for a short flight an try to land.

If you also want to give the SA342 Gazelle helicopter a try download it the helicopter and the prereqs via the links below:

Helicopter:
https://flightsim.to/file/22746/sa342-gazelle

AirlandFS:
https://nl.flightsim.to/file/21417/airlandfs

GMS750:
https://pms50.com/msfs/
